test_large_range:
assert [8, 9, 10] == [9, 10]
  At index 0 diff: 8 != 9
  Left contains one more item: 10
  Full diff:
  - [9, 10]
  + [8, 9, 10]
  ?  +++
test_even_range:
assert [16, 18, 20] == [18, 20]
  At index 0 diff: 16 != 18
  Left contains one more item: 20
  Full diff:
  - [18, 20]
  + [16, 18, 20]
  ?  ++++
